crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET MALWARE Possible Compromised Host AnubisNetworks Sinkhole Cookie Value Snkz
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert http $EXTERNAL_NET any -> $HOME_NET any (msg:"ET MALWARE Possible Compromised Host AnubisNetworks Sinkhole Cookie Value Snkz"; flow:established,to_client; http.cookie; content:"snkz="; pcre:"/^\d{1,3}\x2E\d{1,3}\x2E\d{1,3}\x2E\d{1,3}/R"; threshold:type limit, count 1, seconds 300, track by_src; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:2018141; rev:6; metadata:created_at 2014_02_15, former_category TROJAN, updated_at 2022_08_11;)

alert ( gid:116; sid:424; rev:2; msg:"(eth) truncated ethernet header"; metadata: policy max-detect-ips drop, rule-type decode; classtype:misc-activity;)
